Name: The Guild Garage
Title: Handcrafted Perfection
Desc: David and Janice meet a ton of interesting people and cars during Monterey Car Week.
LongDescription: David and Janice meet a ton of interesting people and cars during Monterey Car Week, including an incredible handcrafted 1949 Talbot-Lago T26 Grand Sport Coupé and the oldest Packard race car in existence, made in 1912.
